#: 2ef5ca69456741e7904406fcf729a5db of
#: tensormesh.distributed.mesh.DistributedMesh:3
msgid ""
"Wraps ``partition_mesh`` to split a global mesh into submeshes, each "
"assigned to a separate device. Each submesh stores an ``orig_nid`` "
"mapping (local node index → global node index) in ``point_data``."
msgstr ""

